ent-SecBreachingHammer = breaching hammer
    .desc = A large, heavy hammer with a long handle, used for breaking stones or other heavy material such as the skulls of violent criminals, also perfect for forcing your way trough airlocks.
ent-SyndieBreachingHammer =  breaching hammer
    .desc = A big, heavy hammer with a long handle. For rocks, skulls, walls, bones — no difference. The last thing you'll hear is a crunch or a grind. Opens airlocks better than SB's ram. Competitors have crash tests and certificates. We have a low-budget snuff parody of American Psycho.
